## ğŸ” Perbedaan Teknis Paling Penting

### ğŸ”¹ Web UI (Token)

* Token = **short-lived credential**
* Bisa **di-rotate kapan saja**
* DNS & routing **di-handle Cloudflare**
* Agent di PC **stateless** (tidak bergantung file lokal)
* **Minim error & anti ribet**

ğŸ‘‰ **Best practice Cloudflare saat ini**

---

### ğŸ”¹ CLI / File (config.yml + json)

* `*.json` = **long-lived credential**
* File **harus dijaga & dibackup**
* File hilang â†’ **tunnel mati**
* Lebih cocok untuk:

  * Server besar / headless
  * Infrastruktur kompleks
  * CI/CD & automation infra

---

## ğŸ§  Analogi Biar Kebayang

### Web UI (Token)

> Seperti **login pakai OTP**
> Hilang HP? â†’ login ulang â†’ beres

### CLI / File

> Seperti **bawa kunci rumah fisik**
> Kunci hilang? â†’ ganti rumah ğŸ˜…

---

## ğŸ¯ Kapan Pakai yang Mana?

### âœ… Pakai **Web UI (Token)** jika:

* PC pribadi / rumahan
* n8n, WAHA, webhook, automation
* Sering ganti PC / reinstall
* Ingin setup cepat & stabil
* Solo dev / UMKM

### âš ï¸ Pakai **CLI / File** jika:

* Server headless / data center
* Banyak environment (dev/staging/prod)
* Infrastruktur otomatis (Terraform, Ansible)
* Tim besar & SOP ketat

